        {
            "title": "Overview",
            "level": 1,
            "blocks":
            [
                {
                    "paragraph": "Snipe Hunter is a control deck that evolved/share a lot of similarities with Wallet Control and Volcanics. The goal of the deck is to achieve complete board control through the aid of Snipe Hunter, Sergeant Electro, and Blaze Accelerator (if you run the Volcanic Shell version)."
                },   
                {
                    "paragraph": "The biggest difference between Snipe Hunter and Wallet Control/Volcanics is that Snipe Hunter fills the role of Sergeant Electro and Blaze Accelerator, as well as other key cards in Wallet Control/Volcanics, with the small price of a 33% chance to fail."
                } 
            ]
        },
