            "title": "Extra Info",
            "level": 1,
            "blocks":
            [
                {
                    "paragraph": "- Snipe Hunter isn't 'meant' to win the dice roll as often as it's 'meant' to force chainable backrow such as Enemy Controller and Red-eyes Spirit."
                },   
                {
                    "paragraph": "- You can use the combination of Volcanic Shell + Switcheroo to go +1."
                },
                {
                    "paragraph": "- Generally you want to keep Snipe Hunter in hand until you have some sort of board control with either backrow and/or Electro."
